# Prompt Interception Feature

- Keep prompt rewrite orchestration in `prompt-rewriter/application`.
- Keep providers/adapters in `prompt-rewriter/infrastructure`.
- Build output sections in fixed order: `input`, `rules`, `skills`, `project`, `memory`.
- Keep each section concise and token-aware.
- Prioritize Python and .NET Core relevance only.
- Expose deterministic outputs for testing and caching.
